BEYOND the DARKNESS sees the signs today with guest Mike Clelland.
Stories from the Messengers: Owls, UFOs and a Deeper Reality

Today we look deeply into the connection, both symbolic and literal, between owls, aliens and UFOs. There is a strangeness to these accounts that defies any simple explanation.
